(42, 'com_content.article.11', '', '2024-04-30 15:12:23', 256, 2737, 'da700fd13711d50011b476a7cad9b266e6732bfd', '{\"id\":11,\"asset_id\":125,\"title\":\"Our Mission & Values\",\"alias\":\"our-mission-values\",\"introtext\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><em><strong>Miss\\u00e3o<\\/strong><\\/em><br \\/><em>Nossa miss\\u00e3o \\u00e9 impulsionar a mudan\\u00e7a positiva atrav\\u00e9s da inova\\u00e7\\u00e3o, excel\\u00eancia e integridade. Buscamos constantemente criar solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es inovadoras que atendam \\u00e0s necessidades de nossos clientes e comunidades, mantendo os mais altos padr\\u00f5es de qualidade e \\u00e9tica em todas as nossas opera\\u00e7\\u00f5es.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><em><strong>Valores<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><em>Integridade<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><em style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Excel\\u00eancia<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><em style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Inova\\u00e7\\u00e3o<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><em style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Respeito<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><em style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Colabora\\u00e7\\u00e3o<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><em style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Sustentabilidade<\\/em><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><em>Estes valores fundamentais guiam nossas a\\u00e7\\u00f5es e decis\\u00f5es, moldando nossa cultura organizacional e impulsionando-nos em dire\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e0 realiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de nossa miss\\u00e3o.<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":11,\"created\":\"2024-04-30 15:12:23\",\"created_by\":256,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-04-30 15:12:23\",\"modified_by\":256,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-04-30 15:12:23\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\